data.title: DiskMINT: Disk Model For INdividual Targets
data.name: DiskMINT
data.description: DiskMINT (Disk Model For INdividual Targets): a tool to estimate disk masses with CO isotopologues

"DiskMINT (Disk Model for INdividual Targets) is a tool for modeling individual disks and deriving more robust disk mass estimates."

"The code contains two parts: (A) a Python3 module ... capable of generating a self-consistent 2D disk structure ... (B) a Fortran code ... of the reduced chemical network focusing on modeling C18O in the disk"
